{"tid":1287471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發完夢瞓醒都要多啲關心身邊嘅人","createTime":"2019-07-05T08:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T08:33:55.000Z","uid":244720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c53c4792c93d638398a837c6bb4c3dfcca4baf28","tid":1287471,"uid":244720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:26:31.000Z","msg":"係呢個月嚟好多人都發夢發到好攰<br />\n嗰一種無力感 或者令人好沮喪<br />\n我相信好多人都一樣<br />\n<br />\n好感謝有咁多人一齊發夢 好團結<br />\n但係希望咁多位香港人 個夢仲未完<br />\n係瞓醒之後返到現實 樂觀啲面對 <br />\n我地仲有希望㗎<br />\n<br />\n返工返學搭車行街 見到一啲望落悶悶不樂嘅人<br />\n有機會佢地係挨埋一面 聽電台聽到喊 等等<br />\n去關心下 帶正能量俾佢 <br />\n就算唔係因為夢而唔開心<br />\n都關懷下大家 香港人要團結 一個都不能少"},{"pid":"e3d94a82ec924029a7c17ee019ee47a824cf8d93","tid":1287471,"uid":244720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:28:01.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d292ca43f3a2483d7d6c0636ff7f6c5f16a2a04d","tid":1287471,"uid":244720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a343c4d54fe84b35eb828e778a00e35ca85cdad5","tid":1287471,"uid":244720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:28:39.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75e807c633b508bd2fe4c0306f276c30c7b6318","tid":1287471,"uid":244720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OnyEwL3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOnyEwL3.png&h=f2961d8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1f35ee45c439e524bac5d412033c976bf59e629","tid":1287471,"uid":244720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQhxRMc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQhxRMc.png&h=f9704bff&s={SIZE}\"